description: This is the account of the Metadimensional Images Collection from 3Magnas and ascii_k. There will be only 4999 unique images in this collection, made out of generation through AI software, and processed with different render tools, like Octane or Unreal Engine. Editions will be smaller and many 1/1 only, so collect it as it is art and at the same time, is fun. Weird Images out of our reality, really magic. Enjoy. For inquiries, contact us at pr@3magnas.no or twitter: @ascii_k
